Package cot_6930_nlp_hw1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NLP_HW1_MP
    Utilizes OpenNLP package tools implemented in the toolsMP package to: 1) Detect sentences in a news article located in - "hw1_files/news_article.txt" 2) Tokenize the text into words 3) Perform part-of-speech (POS) on the text 4) Find name entities including: Dates, Locations, Money, Organizations, Persons, and Time
